com.paypal.merchant.sdk.domain
Interface ManualEntryCardData

All Superinterfaces:
SecureCreditCard
public interface ManualEntryCardData
extends SecureCreditCard

ManualEntryCardData When taking a credit card payment where the card is not present this class is used to contain the card data. The Application fills in this data and provides an instance of this class to the Payment Manager To construct this object please use DomainFactory.newManualEntryCardData(...)
